---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  const posts = [
    {
      slug: 'rise-of-llms',
      title: 'The Rise of Large Language Models',
      content: `
# The Rise of Large Language Models

Large Language Models (LLMs) have revolutionized the field of artificial intelligence, marking a significant breakthrough in natural language processing and understanding. These sophisticated AI models, trained on vast amounts of text data, have demonstrated remarkable capabilities in various tasks, from text generation to complex problem-solving.

## Key Developments

Recent advancements in LLMs have shown impressive improvements in:

- **Context Understanding**: Better grasp of nuanced conversations
- **Reasoning Capabilities**: Enhanced problem-solving abilities
- **Multimodal Integration**: Combining text with image understanding
- **Efficiency**: Reduced training costs and improved performance

## Impact on Industries

The influence of LLMs extends across multiple sectors:

1. **Education**: Personalized learning experiences
2. **Healthcare**: Medical research and documentation
3. **Business**: Customer service and content creation
4. **Research**: Data analysis and hypothesis generation

## Looking Ahead

As we continue to advance in this field, we can expect:

- More specialized models for specific domains
- Improved ethical considerations and safety measures
- Greater accessibility and reduced computational requirements
- Enhanced multilingual capabilities
      `
    }
  ];
  
  return posts.map(post => ({
    params: { slug: post.slug },
    props: { post },
  }));
}

const { post } = Astro.props;
---

<Layout title={post.title}>
  <article class="prose prose-lg prose-invert mx-auto backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
    <div set:html={post.content}></div>
  </article>
</Layout>